Package: openusb-server
Version: 0.1.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: linux-tools-generic | usbip
Maintainer: kman1898
Description: OpenUSB Server - Share USB devices over the network
 OpenUSB is an open-source USB-over-IP solution that allows sharing
 USB devices connected to one machine with other machines on the network.
 This package contains the server daemon (openusbd) and web dashboard.
Homepage: https://github.com/kman1898/openusb
